sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant App as Expo Mobile App
    participant GPS as GPS Service
    participant Storage as Firebase Storage
    participant DB as Firestore Database
    participant Contacts as Emergency Contacts

    Note over User, Contacts: User Task Sequence

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    Note right of User: Create Disaster Report
    User->>App: Select "Report Disaster"
    App->>GPS: Request Current Location
    GPS-->>App: Return Coordinates
    User->>App: Input Details & Attach Media
    App->>Storage: Upload Photos/Videos
    Storage-->>App: Return Media URL
    App->>DB: Save Report Data
    DB-->>App: Success Confirmation
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
    Note right of User: SOS Emergency Flow
    User->>App: Trigger SOS Button
    App->>DB: Fetch Saved Emergency Contacts
    DB-->>App: Return Contact List
    App->>GPS: Get Precise Live Location
    App->>Contacts: Send SOS Alert (SMS/Notification)
    App->>DB: Log SOS Event
    end

    User->>App: Vote (Confirm/Dismiss) Report
    App->>DB: Update Vote Count
    DB-->>App: Refresh UI